{
  "id": "69ee92473991553c15d42f25",
  "title": "ナンプレにおける同じ構造の盤面の代表解についての試行錯誤",
  "created": 1777242769,
  "updated": 1777271174,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ee92473991553c15d42f25",
      "text": "ナンプレにおける同じ構造の盤面の代表解についての試行錯誤",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777242769,
      "updated": 1777242769
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee92910000000000538dc0",
      "text": "code:5区と6区",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777242769,
      "updated": 1777243827
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee98d20000000000538e15",
      "text": " 行区の構成数字が3つ同じ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244370,
      "updated": 1777250129
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee97380000000000538e02",
      "text": " {1  2  3} | {7  8  9}    {1  2  3} | {4  5  6}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777243961,
      "updated": 1777246712
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee973f0000000000538e04",
      "text": " {4  5  6} | {1  2  3}    {4  5  6} | {7  8  9}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777243967,
      "updated": 1777246714
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee92960000000000538dc2",
      "text": "\t{7  8  9} | {4  5  6}    {7  8  9} | {1  2  3}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777242774,
      "updated": 1777246715
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee97c30000000000538e08",
      "text": "\t行区の構成数字が2つ同じ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244100,
      "updated": 1777250126
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee97ca0000000000538e0a",
      "text": " {1  2  3} | {7  8  6}    {1  2  3} | {4  5  9}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244107,
      "updated": 1777246716
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee97ca0000000000538e0b",
      "text": " {4  5  6} | {1  2  9}    {4  5  6} | {7  8  3}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244107,
      "updated": 1777246716
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee97ca0000000000538e0c",
      "text": "\t{7  8  9} | {4  5  3}    {7  8  9} | {1  2  6}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244107,
      "updated": 1777246717
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeaf210000000000538e27",
      "text": "\t行区の構成数字が3つ同じものと2つ同じものは共存させられない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777250082,
      "updated": 1777250409
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeaf700000000000538e28",
      "text": " {1  2  3} | {4  5  6}3   {1  2  3} | {7  8  3}x   ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777250160,
      "updated": 1777250959
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeaf700000000000538e29",
      "text": " {4  5  6} | {1  2  9}2   {4  5  6} | {1  2  9}2   ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777250215,
      "updated": 1777250969
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeaf700000000000538e2a",
      "text": "\t{7  8  9} | {7  8  3}x   {7  8  9} | {4  5  6}3   ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777250160,
      "updated": 1777250967
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb0f60000000000538e2c",
      "text": "code:4区の行区の構成数字は自動で決まる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777250550,
      "updated": 1777250899
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee996b0000000000538e16",
      "text": " 6区の行区の構成数字が5区の行区と同じ → 4区の行区の構成数字も5,6区と同じ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244523,
      "updated": 1777244639
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee98110000000000538e0d",
      "text": " {4  5  6} | {1  2  3} | {7  8  9}    {7  8  9} | {1  2  3} | {4  5  6}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244177,
      "updated": 1777246735
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee98220000000000538e0e",
      "text": " {7  8  9} | {4  5  6} | {1  2  3}    {1  2  3} | {4  5  6} | {7  8  9}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244195,
      "updated": 1777246734
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee98220000000000538e0f",
      "text": "\t{1  2  3} | {7  8  9} | {4  5  6}    {4  5  6} | {7  8  9} | {1  2  3}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244195,
      "updated": 1777246733
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee99920000000000538e17",
      "text": " 6区の行区の構成数字が5区の行区と1つ異なる → 4区の行区の構成数字も5,6区の行区と1つ異なる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244562,
      "updated": 1777244636
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee98220000000000538e10",
      "text": " {4  5  9} | {1  2  3} | {7  8  6}    {7  8  6} | {1  2  3} | {4  5  9}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244195,
      "updated": 1777246750
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee98220000000000538e12",
      "text": " {7  8  3} | {4  5  6} | {1  2  9}    {1  2  9} | {4  5  6} | {7  8  3}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244195,
      "updated": 1777246749
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee98220000000000538e13",
      "text": "\t{1  2  6} | {7  8  9} | {4  5  3}    {4  5  3} | {7  8  9} | {1  2  6}    ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244195,
      "updated": 1777246748
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee98220000000000538e14",
      "text": "code:この構造に帰着できる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777244195,
      "updated": 1777245516
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee9d380000000000538e18",
      "text": " {4  5  *} | {1  2  3} | {7  8  *}",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777245496,
      "updated": 1777252805
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee9d5e0000000000538e1c",
      "text": " {7  8  *} | {4  5  6} | {1  2  *}",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777245534,
      "updated": 1777252803
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee9d610000000000538e1d",
      "text": "\t{1  2  *} | {7  8  9} | {4  5  *}",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777245537,
      "updated": 1777252803
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee9fa20000000000538e1f",
      "text": "\t数字が異なる場合は数字を入れ替えることで対処できる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777246115,
      "updated": 1777246146
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee9d630000000000538e1e",
      "text": "標準化方法",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777245539,
      "updated": 1777246793
    },
    {
      "id": "69eea2490000000000538e21",
      "text": "\t4, 5, 6 区の行区同士で共通する2つの数字を {1, 2}, {4, 5}, {7, 8} とする。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777246793,
      "updated": 1777251014
    },
    {
      "id": "69eea29b0000000000538e23",
      "text": "\t5区の {1, 2} と同じ行区に含まれる数を 3 とする。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777246875,
      "updated": 1777246899
    },
    {
      "id": "69eea2b20000000000538e24",
      "text": "\t5区の {4, 5} と同じ行区に含まれる数を 6 とする。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777246899,
      "updated": 1777246913
    },
    {
      "id": "69eea2b30000000000538e25",
      "text": "\t5区の {7, 8} と同じ行区に含まれる数を 9 とする。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777246899,
      "updated": 1777246915
    },
    {
      "id": "69eea2b30000000000538e26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777246899,
      "updated": 1777246899
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb6e20000000000538e84",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777252067,
      "updated": 1777252067
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb64f0000000000538e74",
      "text": "列に対しても同様の議論ができる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251919,
      "updated": 1777252065
    },
    {
      "id": "69eea28d0000000000538e22",
      "text": "code:行を無視すればこの構造に帰着できる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777246861,
      "updated": 1777251945
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb6980000000000538e7c",
      "text": " |{2 {3 {1 |",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251992,
      "updated": 1777252025
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb6980000000000538e7d",
      "text": " | 5  6  4 |",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251992,
      "updated": 1777252026
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb6980000000000538e7e",
      "text": " | *} *} *}|",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251992,
      "updated": 1777252793
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb6980000000000538e7f",
      "text": " +---------+",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251992,
      "updated": 1777251992
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb6980000000000538e80",
      "text": " |{1 {2 {3 |",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251992,
      "updated": 1777251992
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb6980000000000538e81",
      "text": " | 4  5  6 |",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251992,
      "updated": 1777251992
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb6980000000000538e82",
      "text": " | 7} 8} 9}|",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251992,
      "updated": 1777251992
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb6980000000000538e83",
      "text": " +---------+",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251992,
      "updated": 1777251992
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb3e50000000000538e39",
      "text": " |{3 {1 {2 |",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251302,
      "updated": 1777251992
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb6890000000000538e79",
      "text": " | 6  4  5 |",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251977,
      "updated": 1777251980
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb68c0000000000538e7a",
      "text": " | *} *} *}|",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251980,
      "updated": 1777252788
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb68e0000000000538e7b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777251982,
      "updated": 1777251984
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb86c0000000000538e85",
      "text": "行と列の両方を考慮すると、行区で共通する2つの数字と列区で共通する2つの数字の組み合わせによって幾つかの場合に分かれる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777252461,
      "updated": 1777252518
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb8c40000000000538e87",
      "text": "code:1",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777252549,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538eb4",
      "text": "  .  .  .  |{2 {3 {1 |  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538eb5",
      "text": "  .  .  .  | 5  6  4 |  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538eb6",
      "text": "  .  .  .  | *} *} *}|  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538eb7",
      "text": " ----------+---------+----------",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538eb8",
      "text": " {4  5  *} | 1  2  3 | {7  8  *}",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538eb9",
      "text": " {7  8  *} | 4  5  6 | {1  2  *}",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253930
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538eba",
      "text": " {1  2  *} | 7  8  9 | {4  5  *}",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538ebb",
      "text": " ----------+---------+----------",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538ebc",
      "text": "  .  .  .  |{3 {1 {2 |  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538ebd",
      "text": "  .  .  .  | 6  4  5 |  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538ebe",
      "text": "  .  .  .  | *} *} *}|  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538ebf",
      "text": "\t2,8区は7,8,9に自由度がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538ec0",
      "text": "\t4,6区は3,6,9に自由度がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253670
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebd250000000000538ec1",
      "text": "code:1",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253670,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ed0",
      "text": "  .  .  .  |{2 {3 {1 |  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ed1",
      "text": "  .  .  .  | 8  5  4 |  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253858
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ed2",
      "text": "  .  .  .  | *} *} *}|  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ed3",
      "text": " ----------+---------+----------",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ed4",
      "text": " {4  5  *} | 1  2  3 | {7  8  *}",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ed5",
      "text": " {7  8  *} | 4  6  5 | {1  2  *}",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253926
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ed6",
      "text": " {1  2  *} | 7  8  9 | {4  5  *}",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ed7",
      "text": " ----------+---------+----------",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ed8",
      "text": "  .  .  .  |{3 {1 {2 |  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ed9",
      "text": "  .  .  .  | 5  4  8 |  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538eda",
      "text": "  .  .  .  | *} *} *}|  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538edb",
      "text": "\t2,8区は7,6,9に自由度がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538edc",
      "text": "\t4,6区は3,6,9に自由度がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538edd",
      "text": "code:1",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253832
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ede",
      "text": "  .  .  .  |{2 {1 {7 |  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253880
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538edf",
      "text": "  .  .  .  | 8  5  4 |  .  .  .",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777253832,
      "updated": 1777253862
    },
    {
      "id": "69eebdc70000000000538ee0",
